{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_09_01",
  "title": "miho",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈が生前、私達……Sundanceについて\n話していたことがあると、以前言っていましたよね",
      "startTime": 5.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "その時、彼女はどんなことを話していたか\n私達をどう評していたか、教えていただけませんか",
      "startTime": 13.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（まさかmihoさんが、麻奈の感想を聞いてくるとは）\n（麻奈はなんと言っていただろうか。確か……）",
      "startTime": 22.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一ヶ月前、NexusFes終了直後",
      "startTime": 28.4163606372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.9073230744
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.9073230744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんも、今日はイベントお疲れ様でした\nいや本当に、無事に終わって良かったですよ……",
      "startTime": 34.1000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんもスリクスを続けると仰ってくれましたし\nこれで俺もなんとか、安心して寝られます",
      "startTime": 41.5246193502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.6808604243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方の安眠はどうでもいいですけど\nフェスについては、早速記事になっているようですね",
      "startTime": 47.7162116689,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2752.473290499999,
          "startTime": 47.4333337148
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.2118127508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ふっ。世界を股にかけて活躍するアイドルというのも\nなかなかいい響きですね",
      "startTime": 56.1828783355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.08510081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう言えば、mihoさんの経歴を拝見したんですが\n以前も、台湾ツアーに行かれたことがあるそうですね",
      "startTime": 62.1666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その時はどんな感じだったんですか？\n台湾はご飯もうまそうですし、それだけでも羨まし……",
      "startTime": 68.6000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.3952415151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに以前、台湾を回ったことはありますよ\nただ葉ちゃんはいなくて、私一人でしたけど",
      "startTime": 77.0930190406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　……えっと、余計なこと聞いたみたいで",
      "startTime": 80.4515002889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.9919332824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……葉ちゃんが入院している間も\n私を暇にさせておく訳にはいかないと言われましてね",
      "startTime": 88.7334520342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "休養当初は、しばらく入院すれば治ると思ってましたし\nまた一緒にステージに立てると思っていたんですよ",
      "startTime": 97.8001187009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "でも日本に戻ったら、葉ちゃんはもう酷く痩せてて……",
      "startTime": 100.902318605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.902318605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "ツアー中の私を心配させないように\n元気な顔の写真ばっかり、送ってきていたんです",
      "startTime": 109.0333388011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.4926809949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……なんで私、友達を置いていってしまったんだろう\nこうなると分かっていたら、側を離れなかったのに",
      "startTime": 118.2334520342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん……\nすみません、話し辛いことを",
      "startTime": 123.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.4455632849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "別に、貴方の無神経は今に始まったことでもないですし\nこれ以上株の下がりようもないので、安心して下さい",
      "startTime": 131.7085794134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.4464824997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "……ここで解散しても構わないと、この前は思ったけど\nまた一人で取り残されるのは、やっぱり嫌ね",
      "startTime": 139.9085692408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "こんなこと、あの子達には絶対に言わないけど",
      "startTime": 143.8732286774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん？　すみません、よく聞こえなくて",
      "startTime": 147.8560403033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 147.8560403033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "私は何も言っていません\nおそらく貴方の気のせいでしょう",
      "startTime": 154.2653836252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――帰国後",
      "startTime": 157.2233420058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 158.3320502919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n相談があるのですが、少しお時間をいただけますか？",
      "startTime": 160.7987169585,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 158.966650772
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああはい、大丈夫ですよ\nそれで、相談というのは……",
      "startTime": 167.066650772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "私達の、新曲についての相談なのですが",
      "startTime": 169.7851547244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "新曲……\n『Bittersweet Echo』のことですか？",
      "startTime": 175.1333174387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　もしかしてVENUSグランプリのことですか\n出場用の曲を、あの曲から変更したいとか……",
      "startTime": 181.8333174387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "いえ『Bittersweet Echo』ではなくて\n昔の私達の曲を、カバーするという話です",
      "startTime": 189.4329573633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、アメリカでfranさんから聞いてます\nSundanceの曲を、スリクスで歌うんですよね",
      "startTime": 196.4333174387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "どの曲にするかは、もう決まってるんですか？",
      "startTime": 199.5438628359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "franとkanaにはこれから確認しますが……\n『Friend Glass』にしようと思っています",
      "startTime": 206.4333119709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲は当時、私達の代名詞みたいなものでしたし\n私自身、思い入れもありますから",
      "startTime": 213.8143857799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。関係者には俺から問い合わせておきます\n多分、使用許可は問題なく出ると思いますよ",
      "startTime": 221.066650772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "よろしくお願いします",
      "startTime": 224.3525243445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "『Friend Glass』かぁ、懐かしいですね\n俺も関係者席で聴いた覚えがありますけど",
      "startTime": 229.8333164214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "お二人の絆と言うか、仲がいいのが伝わってきて\nこちらも温かい気分になるような曲でした",
      "startTime": 237.5666453043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "貴方から、昔の曲の感想を聞くのは初めてですね\n一応、ありがとうございますと言っておきます",
      "startTime": 244.9541144214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk022.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……今更、昔の曲を引っ張り出してきて\nそれがいいことなのかどうかも分かりませんけど",
      "startTime": 252.9999786376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "俺は昔好きだった曲を、また聴けたら嬉しいですけどね\nそういうファンの人は多いんじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 260.366650772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_01-mhk023.m4a",
      "text": "そのくらいのお気楽さで、済めばいいんですけど\n……ファンだった人達の反応こそ、不安なんですよ",
      "startTime": 267.5203265352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 271.7536354544,
      "sfxList": []
